Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:01.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,take my hand in marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:11.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.37,Hand,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\frx12\fry344\move(796.363636,406.5,670.909091,406.5)\frz13.184\c&H46372D&}Takasu Ryuuji's Pen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.75,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:24.58,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan gave birth to so many puppies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,They're your kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A dream, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:43.43,Hand,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&HD8C1BC&\frz19.498\be1\move(483.636364,168,556.363636,238.5)}~I gave birth to puppies!~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:43.43,Hand,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz19.202\be1\c&HD8C1BC&\move(447.272727,103.5,520,174)}True Story of Fear\Nfrom the Islands of Japan:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's finally summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having these dreams because of the stupid DVDs we rented.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a dream, that's one awful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You were a dog, and my husband was the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.99,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,it was a horrible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:06.04,Ep Titles,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(883.636364,544.5)\fad(400,400)\fs48}You, who are going to the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A premonition?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:10.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was a warning, telling me that if I don't work out a counter-plan, {\i1}that{\i0} future awaits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That dream was...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to change the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,one side should fully support the other starting with the trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Decide who's doing what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:34.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, be careful when using the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stir the rice bran once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to change Inko-chan's water in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Read the rest in the note I left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.79,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Going? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I? On a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Yacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the weather's going to be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm counting on you... for {\i1}that{\i0} plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's your win, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Get this thing off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.86,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for that dumb dog getting involved, I would have won!{trespassing didnt fit here :}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:23.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was punishment for setting up a match in something you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Nothing good ever comes out of anything involving dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Still... will it really go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:36.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,When this trip is over, your relationship with Minorin will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.10,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.64,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Simply great!{this stays or RAGE}{furthermore... ts it to the colors of the rainbow ("fabulous")}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Where's the energy?! Make some noise! {Missing line after this where Ryuuji says "Y-Yeah..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.35,Alternative,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.06,Alternative,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{uwaaa}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.07,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,My, the weather has become perfect for an outing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.11,Alternative,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{micha ikemasen}Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.78,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, A-min's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.91,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.62,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.39,Alternative,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.99,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.62,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those guys? There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.54,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You're two minutes late, Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.59,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, A-min!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, stupid chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.14,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't run away, stupid chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.72,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, we're right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.73,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.32,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a plum in this that makes it super plum!{yes she's doing a horrible pun here - kaze approves yet kinda wants to reword it}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.99,Alternative,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.32,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Want to marry into my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.49,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.74,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.16,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.08,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,it seems Aisaka-san didn't come. Is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.46,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, go get in touch with—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.79,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The stupid chi' is awake?{starting this episode, Taiga is shortening down stupid chihuahua to stupid 'hua -> bakachiwawa = bakachi}{so it should be "stupid chi'" to match accordingly which is pronounced the same for the dog name anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.88,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were sleeping with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:01.51,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight when we're on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what have you been doing during summer break so far, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.85,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.39,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you started working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.65,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities, work, club activities, work, club activities, club activities, work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,club activities, work, club activities, work, club...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.03,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.45,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:26.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:36.29,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just now, I heard "senpai" in a strange voice! Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sampled from CD's with more to them than just what they advertised — a collection of spirit voices.{いわくつきのCDから集めた心霊音声集}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.96,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.63,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No~! I've been called out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.97,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka likes those kinds of horror things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.93,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I might like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.39,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.52,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's also rather surprising that Kushieda's scared of eerie things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.73,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of it, I'm scared of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.23,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super scared of it, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.27,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than super scared, you could say I'm incredibly scared—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:05.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you see, is {\i1}really{\i0} scared of horror movies, spirits, and occult things in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:11.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to scare Minorin to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:16.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're going to save her when she's at the peak of her fear.{I'm not sure how you say when someone's at the very height of being frightened in english, so I tried.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,With a, "I will protect Kushieda!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the "Scare Minorin, Enter the White Knight!" plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Scary things are absolutely forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.26,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... how far do we have to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.04,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it already, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:55.54,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.96,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go around the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.75,Default,AMi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going that way and I think we'll be on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.05,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,This is A-min's vacation home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.46,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be staying here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.97,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.88,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:12.51,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But... we've got to clean the place up first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.39,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's been here since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since last year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like it'll be one hell of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:24.28,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We've got this pretty sea right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.28,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{souji nanka}Let's leave cleaning up for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.45,Alternative,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We can clean later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.28,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too... What about you, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I cleaning all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.02,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.72,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.27,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,kinda looks like someone's head, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:05.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, it's a floating corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.57,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! I've been soaked in corpse water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.32,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.24,Alternative,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry, Minorin! That might be seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.58,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wah, then it's a seaweed corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.58,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You really came, Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.25,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What should I do?! I've been soaked in seaweed corpse water!{I can't make out any more of these lines.... maybe omit them?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.45,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.08,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have Takasu come without his good friend coming along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.71,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about this? What about the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.92,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.42,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.97,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.01,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ami said to go out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.26,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's a bike in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:37.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, take Taiga with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:42.98,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Take Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.11,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:48.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.76,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.16,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You finally had a chance to be alone together. {re-time to after the sigh}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I had an idea, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:09.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Before they come back, we've got to find somewhere suitable to play out {\i1}that{\i0} plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're just embarrassed, just admi—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mosquito there, a mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say "somewhere suitable"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,a bathroom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta clean here too—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.82,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.48,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll get out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.57,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're really bold, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.87,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in while a girl's showering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.00,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We can keep it a secret from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you say—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.63,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.09,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Clean the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.26,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.47,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?! It's a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Stupid chi' did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Making it sound like she was taking a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with a man's pure heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And? Did you finish investigating the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.53,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got tricked by the likes of the stupid chi'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And while I'm at it, I'm going to tell her off as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stupid chi'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid chi' was actually in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid chi' was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,BOOM!{right breast}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And BOOM!{left breast}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And here, it was EXPLODING!{ami doesn't shave downstairs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.78,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You sure bought a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:55.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting the bike away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.99,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'll carry them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda did the shopping, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.50,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.13,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right now, something... on my — on my neck... {re-time to "ima"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sou da yo ne...}Y-You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.09,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sou da yo ne!}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.80,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{ima tashika ni}Something definitely touched me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{nuru tte iuka}Something slippery... like seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.77,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{y-yappari}I-It really does smell like seaweed! It's seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.56,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{wakame ni maki-}Like an animal spirit entwined in seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.90,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{rakko? wakame-}A sea otter? When it comes to being entwined in seaweed, it has to be the corpse of a sea otter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kawa no poketto}A sea otter with its stomach pocket filled with scallops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.65,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{rakko to wakame no noroi da!}It's the curse of the sea otter and seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.16,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer it spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.99,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat it if it's not sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure your portion is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.21,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving special treatment to Aisaka-san again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.92,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That will get you hated by girls, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.42,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,By Minori-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:56.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.09,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You called for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Almost done? You're skilled, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to add the roux.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys have to prepare for dinner—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.14,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, already preparing for supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.44,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can help out with putting out plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.03,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.83,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I heard Takasu's voice, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.24,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,The girls were here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.20,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.83,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.75,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.62,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:37.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You narcissistic heaven-sent child! Give me a nude shot!{don't like child here}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.92,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! Quit it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.09,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying while looking like that, pretending to be modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.59,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.60,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{nanka ima}Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.81,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kurokute}something black and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{wasattoshita}rather lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably a seaweed spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.69,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.27,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.28,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, you're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.24,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.11,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.58,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There's an evil spirit lurking in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.58,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Make the curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.67,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{uun to}{\i1}really{\i0} spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.72,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it looks so tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I made it with what I had available, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{kushieda no}as per Kushieda's request, I've made it as spicy as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.14,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.02,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.56,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.06,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's weally dewishus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.44,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as spicy as I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.86,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You want to try it too, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,SPICY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.88,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten spicy—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.00,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,—in my throat! Rather, it's hot! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.17,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.26,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I have received this meal with impact!{yeah this weird but she uses GATSUN (impact) + itadakimasu - since itadakimasu = receive/take food/drink - this works.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.84,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There it is again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.26,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.26,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-spicy! It's super-delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.19,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It does indeed have a strange quality to it that makes you keep eating it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.61,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... starting to feel strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's seconds too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.28,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.36,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.37,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.33,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because I ate spicy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I want some stomach medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach's hurting? But I didn't bring med—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.13,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, are you feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.09,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some stomach medicine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.30,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's in my room, wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Th... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.64,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha — eh — wai —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chance to be alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.68,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.06,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.82,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.90,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan's stomach hurts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.61,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.87,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.95,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You were spacing out, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Observing you never gets boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.83,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're just really complicated.{I'm getting much out of this one line because of the novels, where they elaborate on his inner thoughts of ami. I'm especially going to note this line in the notes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.38,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.47,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, if you'd like, we could go to the beach toge—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun, could you get that glass for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.07,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Was it enough water?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.78,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Prob... ably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.58,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.45,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Aisaka in pain makes me hurt too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.83,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. If it hurts, would you like to lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You... have amazing cleaning techniques, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.68,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm doing it all the time at work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:13.72,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun's curry was prepared with splendor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.68,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.39,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something great as thanks for helping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.69,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret from everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun... is the green tea flavor good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Not so much with the azuki one.{she means the green tea version was better than the azuki one}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.49,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's packed with stars here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you'd call a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-Kushieda, d-do you have boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:57.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The seaweed spirit from earlier... you think it's still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:57.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.77,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{takasu-kun wa}Takasu-kun, have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.23,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yuurei mita koto aru?}ever seen a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No. I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{watashi wa}I believe that ghosts exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.86,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{demo}But I have never seen one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{mita koto ga aru-}and I don't believe the stories from people who have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.10,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sore to sa-}And then, you see, I think of something else the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:23.37,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{watashi mo itsuka}I believe that one day I'll be in love, get married, and be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:27.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kedo jissai}But there's nobody who has had it spelled out like that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:33.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{you no naka no}I think that the existence of people in the world who are meant to love one another is a bit farfetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.80,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{datte watashi ni}I mean, I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:42.27,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yappari yuurei}"There really isn't anything like ghosts, so I'll never see one in my life" — is how I have resigned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:47.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara shitsumon}And because of that, there is no answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.32,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{takasu-kun wa}What about Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.48,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yuurei mieru-}Are you someone who can see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{ore wa-}I think... I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:17:00.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara shinrei spotto}Because of that, I go to places with spirits and I watch scary DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{ore, omoun dakedo sa}You see, I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{reikan ga aru yatsu}people who are sensitive to spirits would be shocked the first time they saw one, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{mita kedo}I think there are people who have seen them, but then they tried to deny their existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:17.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{gyaku ni douryokushite}and on the other hand, there are those who put in an effort to finally be able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:23.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara omae mo}Because of that, I think that you don't have to resign yourself to never seeing one in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.35,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.44,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought it was a UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:44.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be great if you could see ghosts sometime, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.35,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think that there's a ghost out there that wants you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why there were lots of strange things that happened today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.93,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's appealing to me! The seaweed spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.43,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll see them one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji. I think my stomach's all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm full! So full!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about {\i1}that{\i0} plan, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.72,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing your part properly at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the support this time around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Am I ever tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:49.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:56.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking about how happy I'd be after spending an entire day with Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,but I was so nervous I could die an early death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Though when I'm with you, I'm completely fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:06.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This room is so big, yet we're sitting this close to one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the habits of being in a small apartment have stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.72,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That dream was... rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I put my bag here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What is... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And it's somewhat slippery...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was in my bag... yet when I touched it earlier, it was still warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,as if someone had just been wearing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,My room's weird too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,On my pillow, there was long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was prob—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a dream... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a continuation of that dream, living in a dog house, giving birth to dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if we close our eyes, we'll wake up sometime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wake up! We'll wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:24.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:35.04,Ep Titles 2,TS,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(329.090909,195)\be1}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:35.04,Ep Titles 2,TS,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(1056.363636,546)}Fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.87,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.95,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Horror movies are scary! Ghosts are scary! Monsters are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.46,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,But... the scariest might be UFOs...
